111 (D) In the absence of an approved report, the chairperson may file with the Secretary
112 of the Senate and the Clerk of the House of Representatives copies of the minutes of the
113 meetings of the commission in lieu thereof.
114 (7) Abolishment. The commission shall stand abolished on December 1, 2026.
